{"tid":936610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新垃圾桶設計屬「機密」","createTime":"2018-12-11T01:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T08:29:51.000Z","uid":10540,"like":2,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"55644cfdfaa21b585ade2202a639bbb4dabe66a7","tid":936610,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:52:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20181211/s00046/fe4a812a0da7364be2b07b1ce245d8d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20181211%2Fs00046%2Ffe4a812a0da7364be2b07b1ce245d8d9.jpg&h=047a4d5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有委員話噚日開會討論嘅優化設計，同今年5月委員會選出嘅最佳方案（圖）分別不大。圖為早前構思圖。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】為配合都市固體廢物收費，公共空間回收及垃圾收集設施改造督導委員會（簡稱「桶改會」）噚日召開閉門會議，會後環保署發出新聞稿，話會議討論優化設計，委員仲有得試用實體新垃圾桶模型，但就無提供照片供傳媒刊登，搞到件事好神秘。有委員話政府為咗保密，唔單止無提供討論文件，仲唔畀委員影相，有委員接受Emily查詢時更引述政府話新設計係「機密資料」，唔可以透露任何嘢，唔講仲以為係咩偉大發明。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>明年5至8月諮詢公眾</strong><br />\n政府於2016年2月成立「桶改會」，花咗差唔多3年，開過7次會，直至噚日先搞到一個個垃圾桶同回收桶嘅實物畀委員試用，唔通真係精雕細琢？<br />\n<br />\n政府透過新聞稿話，新款回收桶同垃圾桶嘅設計符合人體工學，外觀更協調；至於喺室內場地使用嘅桶，就會用透明物料製造，市民會更容易掌握回收物類別，有利源頭分類。<br />\n<br />\n有委員同Emily講，其實優化設計同上次開會其中一個方案好相似，即係「細口」垃圾桶，以及「一體化」回收桶，委員普遍對新設計收貨。據悉，政府明年1至4月會就新設計諮詢前線員工及設計界等持份者意見，5至8月諮詢公眾，到時新設計就會曝光。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20181211/s00002/1544467372950/%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E6%A1%B6%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E5%B1%AC%E3%80%8C%E6%A9%9F%E5%AF%86%E3%80%8D?fbclid=IwAR1uLrnc0gZHQYQL7ID-ehGZ_ibrCNrT2t5Tf4FICXBCfybGHocbv3CXeWE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20181211%2Fs00002%2F1544467372950%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE%25E6%25A1%25B6%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25AF%2586%25E3%2580%258D%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1uLrnc0gZHQYQL7ID-ehGZ_ibrCNrT2t5Tf4FICXBCfybGHocbv3CXeWE&d=nP9n0xxTvs6c74aFzLq0LBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=3ecee8b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20181211%2Fs00002%2F1544467372950%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE%25E6%25A1%25B6%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25AF%2586%25E3%2580%258D%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1uLrnc0gZHQYQL7ID-ehGZ_ibrCNrT2t5Tf4FICXBCfybGHocbv3CXeWE&h=fa73757c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20181211/s00002/1544467372950/%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E6%A1%B6%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E5%B1%AC%E3%80%8C%E6%A9%9F%E5%AF%86%E3%80%8D?fbclid=IwAR1uLrnc0gZHQYQL7ID-ehGZ_ibrCNrT2t5Tf4FICXBCfybGHocbv3CXeWE</a>"},{"pid":"9513cc2ca0448d2379c0d3af2763f9962235d18e","tid":936610,"uid":135753,"like":137,"dislike":1,"score":136,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjh8jmo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbjh8jmo.png&h=afe9bbc8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20087db6b2e9f4e0299c8567b52a0e6e152d7c73","tid":936610,"uid":49392,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:57:41.000Z","msg":"新劉江華線條似乎幾適合做尿兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d188fc4967a77f4ff5c39c977e674744ce3ddcf","tid":936610,"uid":88263,"like":84,"dislike":2,"score":82,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:57:46.000Z","msg":"咁設計，落雨咪入撚晒水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nOn99<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e361a5eb0e7366ae1d503747d96d7325394f9919","tid":936610,"uid":150544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:02:26.000Z","msg":"高官又有花紅出"},{"pid":"eb68f894fc07177567bca60201d939788ffe1ffc","tid":936610,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"20087db6b2e9f4e0299c8567b52a0e6e152d7c73","tid":936610,"uid":49392,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"201